Merkel Describes Lagarde as ‘Excellent” Personality, DPA Says

-- B y   S h e e n a g h   M a t t h e w s
-- 
2011-05-21T10:22:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-21/merkel-describes-lagarde-as-excellent-personality-dpa-says.html
German  Chancellor Angela Merkel 
described French Finance Minister  Christine Lagarde  as an
“excellent and experienced person” while stopping short of
naming her as a candidate to head the  International Monetary
Fund ,  Deutsche Presse-Agentur  said.  The chancellor, speaking today at a meeting of her
Christian Social Union Bavarian allies, said there is broad
support for  Europe  to put up a candidate, according to DPA.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sheenagh Matthews in Frankfurt at 
 smatthews6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at 
 bkammel@bloomberg.net  